df['WindDir3pm'] = le.fit_transform(df['WindDir3pm'])
df['RainToday'] = le.fit_transform(df['RainToday'])
df['RainTomorrow'] = le.fit_transform(df['RainTomorrow'])

abc_probs = abc_probs[:, 1]
xgb_probs = xgb_probs[:, 1]
In [26]:
from sklearn.metrics import roc_curve, roc_auc_score
In [28]:
lr_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, lr_probs)
dt_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, dt_probs)
rf_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, rf_probs)
abc_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, abc_probs)
xgb_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, xgb_probs)

print('XGBoost : AUROC = %.3f' % (xgb_auc))

ROC ( Receiver Operating Characteristic Curve )¶

In [45]:
plt.plot(rf_fpr, rf_tpr, marker='.', label='Random Forest (AUROC = %0.3f)' % rf_auc)
plt.plot(abc_fpr, abc_tpr, marker='.', label='Ada Boosting (AUROC = %0.3f)' % abc_auc)
plt.plot(dt_fpr, dt_tpr, linestyle='--', label='Decision Tree (AUROC = %0.3f)' % dt_auc)
plt.plot(xgb_fpr, xgb_tpr, marker='.', label='Xgboost (AUROC = %0.3f)' % xgb_auc)
plt.plot(lr_fpr, lr_tpr, marker='.', label='Logistic Regression (AUROC = %0.3f)' % lr_auc)
